= Story Guide =

'''The 7th Saga''' follows one of seven apprentices seeking ancient Runes.

__TOC__

== Premise ==

King Domaric of Lemele sends seven apprentices on a quest to find the seven Runes scattered across the world. Each apprentice has their own reasons for seeking the Runes.

