== Gameplay Tips ==

=== Grinding ===

The 7th Saga requires significant grinding:
* Random encounters are tough
* Level difference matters greatly
* Metal enemies give high EXP (but flee)

=== Party Selection ===

{| class="wikitable"
! Strategy !! Recommended Partners
|-
| Balanced || Fighter + Healer
|-
| Offense || Two strong attackers
|-
| Magic || Spellcasters together
|}

=== Rival Preparation ===

Before facing other apprentices:
* Be well-leveled
* Best available equipment
* Full healing items
* Know their patterns

